{"tid":1275001,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有感而發］71一事","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T07:45:11.000Z","uid":248333,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c52073f25d21b7d10ac8bb0b994042de1238c6a","tid":1275001,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:50:32.000Z","msg":"首先多謝first aid，走嚟走去幫助受咗傷嘅人同陪<br />\n<br />\n咗我地成日。<br />\n<br />\n    第二係社工，我地有人要上救護車佢地即刻9秒9<br />\n<br />\n飛過嚟陪傷者去醫院。<br />\n  <br />\n    第三係救護員，我地一有咩事就開架車過嚟送我<br />\n<br />\n地去醫院，就算條馬路幾窄都好。<br />\n  <br />\n    第四係前線嘅義士，全副親民裝備去衝激立法會<br />\n<br />\n真係唔係痴線就真係痴撚線。<br />\n<br />\n    第五係中間果堆，應該叫做囤積派掛，佢地會用<br />\n<br />\n大聲公一傳十十傳百咁講有咩需要有咩唔需要，需<br />\n<br />\n要就傳上去，唔需要就分好類等下一波攻勢。<br />\n<br />\n    第六係尾尾個堆購物派/後援派，我地一需要啲咩<br />\n<br />\n就即刻買番嚟比我地，勁快手買到果隻。仲有咩鐵<br />\n<br />\n馬水馬交通錐推/拉咗成日由後面送到前線真係真心<br />\n<br />\n服。<br />\n<br />\n    最後再次多謝曬咁多位，如果我漏咗多謝邊個請<br />\n<br />\n講出嚟，我會一一多謝番佢地或者唔該你地係下面<br />\n<br />\n留言幫我多謝佢地！！<br />\n<br />\nBtw呢一兩個月我地有開心有好唔開心！經過依一次我先知原來香港人真係可以對其他人好好，希望大家可以繼續努力團結落去半個都嫌好撚多！！ <br />\n<br />\n  原諒我係依家緊張嘅氣氛度講而啲野！"},{"pid":"28ec16b6522fe4bf1da0d32bb79f05b42e3d8cd5","tid":1275001,"uid":11331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"唔好客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30d81240a9eb73f0991463f44a63928e6ef5b20","tid":1275001,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:51:49.000Z","msg":"手機排得差 唔好意思 唔係有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95846348dde6105bdc2e5f29035e8cec9614d88","tid":1275001,"uid":44870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"你唔記得多謝埋你自己有份行出黎"},{"pid":"0b2214bcd62815e369672e4d6dda4d6d551533c7","tid":1275001,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95846348dde6105bdc2e5f29035e8cec9614d88","tid":1275001,"uid":44870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"你唔記得多謝埋你自己有份行出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0bad0c7d1c053b2456dfa9008adf490ac7cdf8","tid":1275001,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"我屌啱啱先睇到，班狗有冇甘撚狗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要冇事呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81402e2b393eb7f5f4c6b12c7146ffd1eb8dc039","tid":1275001,"uid":182774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25cb488a8c29f7a8b274165f9cfa8a0134de33b1","tid":1275001,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:49:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72a48b407d6b7d26d7502bc999e23c48a45574de","tid":1275001,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"推一推 想比人知我啲感想"},{"pid":"f4f78a4a2a54277f4d0c1abffc8edae0b18b029c","tid":1275001,"uid":248333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a